# Draw-from-winning-position regression seeds — Phase 12 (#129)
# Format (PGN-extracted): <fen-4-fields> bm <last_san>; c0 "<label>";
# Format (manual seeds):  <fen-4-fields> c0 "<label>";
# Append-only: never remove entries unless bug is confirmed fixed AND a regression test covers it.
